  <p>Dear Sir s<br />
To whom it may concern, and with all due respect. &#8221; good luck  with the Irish court case&#8221; I am working class but I am a passionate remainer. It is becoming more and more apparent, that Brexit and Trump are of the same movement. It&#8217;s all politics based on hate, that has exploited the anger and wrath of the people.<br />
